    "followup_output": "- followup_message: Hi Rana, I just wanted to check in and see how you're doing, especially with your wife's pregnancy. We're working on getting you the help you need, and I'll make sure to follow up with the NGOs and schemes that can assist you with the expenses. Please take care of yourself and your wife, and don't hesitate to reach out if you need anything.\n- recommended_followup_days: 2",
